  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Good living through access to safe drinking water in Tapacari</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To improve the general state of health in 12 villages in the municipality of Tapacari. This is done by constructing water supply systems that provide safe drinking water in sufficient quality and quantity and by spreading knowledge of adequate hygienic pra
ctices through workshops and training of communal health promoters. In addition the sustainability of the results of the previous project (42802301)is assured.</narrative>
